To implement the **Frozen Expanse** map, I have designed a large-scale 1v1 competitive layout that adheres to your specific winter theme and strategic requirements.

The following code defines the new map in `SkirmishMapPresets.cs`. It includes 14 high-ground plateaus, 30 clay walls, 15 resource nodes, and 31 terrain features, all balanced with diagonal mirror symmetry.

### Implementation Steps

1.  Open `Assets/_InsectWars/Scripts/Data/SkirmishMapPresets.cs`.
2.  Update the `GetAll()` method to include the new map.
3.  Add the `CreateFrozenExpanse()` static method at the bottom of the class.

#### 1. Updated `GetAll()` Method
```csharp
public static SkirmishMapDefinition[] GetAll()
{
    if (s_maps != null) return s_maps;
    s_maps = new[] { CreateThornBasin(), CreateLalush(), CreateFrozenExpanse() };
    return s_maps;
}
```

#### 2. New `CreateFrozenExpanse()` Method
